{"article_id":"9o4i8tVwIA7T1nRu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Obama administration and three prominent governors","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"- two of them Democrats -","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"are at odds over whether or not people","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"returning to the US from Ebola-stricken countries in West Africa","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"should be quarantined .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"New York , New Jersey , and Illinois","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"- led , respectively , by Governors Andrew Cuomo","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"( D ) ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Chris Christie","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"( R ) ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"and Pat Quinn","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"( D ) -","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"have ordered mandatory quarantine for those","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"deemed `` high risk ''","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"of carrying the disease .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Generally speaking ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that means health care workers or anybody else","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"who has had direct contact with an Ebola patient in Sierra Leone , Guinea , or Liberia .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"On Saturday , Florida Gov . Rick Scott","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"( R )","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"ordered twice daily monitoring for anyone","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"returning from places","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention designates as affected by Ebola .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Gov . Scott said","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"if the state health department determines","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"any of those monitored are at a high risk","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"of contracting the disease ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"the state will take further action","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"to protect those individuals and the rest of Florida with a mandatory quarantine .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Appearing on five television news shows Sunday ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Dr. Anthony Fauci , director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases , warned","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that mandatory , 21-day quarantining of medical workers","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"returning from West Africa","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"is unnecessary","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"and could discourage volunteers from going there","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"to help fight the spread of the disease .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"`` If you put everyone in one basket , even people","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"who are clearly no threat ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"then we have the problem of the disincentive of people","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that we need , ''","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Dr. Fauci said on ABC 's This Week .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` Let 's not forget","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"the best way","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"to stop this epidemic","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"and protect America","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"is to stop it in Africa ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"and you can really help stopping it in Africa","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"if we have our people , our heroes , the health care workers ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"go there","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and help us to protect America . ''","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"UN Ambassador Samantha Power weighed in too ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"telling NBC News","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that returning American health care workers should be `` treated like conquering heroes","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"and not stigmatized for the tremendous work","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that they have done . ''","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Amb . Power ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"who is traveling in West Africa ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"quarantine plans in New York , New Jersey , and Illinois are `` haphazard and not well thought out . ''","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` We can not take measures here","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that are going to impact our ability","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"to flood the zone , ''","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"Power said .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"`` We have to find the right balance","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"between addressing the legitimate fears","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"that people have","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"and encouraging and incentivizing these heroes . ''","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"A senior administration official told the New York Times","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"the decision by the governors was \" uncoordinated , very hurried , an immediate reaction to the New York City case","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that doesn ' t comport with science . \"","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"New York 's quarantine measures were announced","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"after Dr. Craig Spencer returned to New York City","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"from treating Ebola victims in Guinea for Doctors Without Borders .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"He was admitted to Bellevue Hospital Center last Thursday","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"to be treated for Ebola symptoms .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"The US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention recommends voluntary quarantines .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"appearing on `` Fox News Sunday , ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Gov . Christie defended his action","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"in ordering a mandatory quarantine .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"when you 're dealing with something as serious as this","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"you can count on a voluntary system , ''","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"`` This is the government 's job . ''","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"this is a policy","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"that will become a national policy sooner or later , ''","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"he added .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"`` It 's too serious a situation","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"to leave it to the honor system of compliance , ''","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Gov . Cuomo said recently .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Meanwhile , Kaci Hickox , the first nurse","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"forcibly quarantined in New Jersey under the state 's new policy ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"said in a telephone interview with CNN","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"that her isolation at a hospital was `` inhumane , ''","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"adding :","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"`` We have to be very careful about letting politicians make health decisions . ''","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Ms. Hickox has twice tested negative for Ebola","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"and has exhibited no evidence of the disease .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"She told CNN","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"that she was put in an isolation tent inside University Hospital in Newark","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"where she has no shower , no flushable toilet ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"and was given paper scrubs","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"to wear .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":109,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":110,"text":"`` While we understand","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"that the required quarantine is an inconvenience ,","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"it is our primary goal to make sure the patient is as comfortable as possible , ''","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"hospital spokesperson Stacie Newton told CNN .","depth":4},{"id":114,"text":"`` We have given our prompt attention","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"to provide the patient with basic needs","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"and to accommodate additional requests","depth":6},{"id":117,"text